Preference:
  Interface: postion bottom->right
  Terminal: Scroll on output/Override Geany keybindings/Follow path of the current file/Execute programs in the VTE
  Keybindings: change it to what you like.

Build: 
  Set Build Commands:
    Compile: g++ -std=c++17 -Wshadow -Wall -o "%e" "%f" -O2 -Wno-unused-result -w
    Build: g++ -std=c++17 -w -Wshadow -Wall -o "%e" "%f" -g -fsanitize=address -fsanitize=undefined -D_GLIBCXX_DEBUG -D LOCAL
    


